jasima.core.simulation

类 Simulation.SimPrintMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • jasima.core.simulation.Simulation.SimPrintMessage
  • 封闭类:
    Simulation

    public static class Simulation.SimPrintMessage
extends java.lang.Object
    Simulation.SimPrintMessages are produced whenever print() or trace() is called during a simulation to produce status/debug messages. They are passed to print listeners registered with a simulation for further processing.
    另请参阅:
    ConsolePrinter, TraceFileProducer
